---
---

<section class="exec-section exec-section-auto exec-type-journey-section">
  <div class="exec-inner">
    <div class="type-journey">
      <div class="type-journey-title">The Transformation: Type 1 to Type 3 Organization</div>
      <div class="type-journey-sub">Machina does not just give you software. It moves your entire organization up the operational maturity curve — and that is what makes you defensible.</div>

      <div class="type-stages">
        <div class="type-stage exec-reveal">
          <div class="type-badge">1</div>
          <div class="type-name">Fully Manual</div>
          <div class="type-desc">Every task requires a human. Scaling means hiring. Margins compress as you grow. This is where most MCOs are today.</div>
          <div class="type-metrics">
            <div class="type-metric">High headcount per patient</div>
            <div class="type-metric">Low margins at scale</div>
            <div class="type-metric">Fragile operations</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="type-stage exec-reveal">
          <div class="type-badge">2</div>
          <div class="type-name">AI-Assisted</div>
          <div class="type-desc">AI supports your team with suggestions, reminders, and partial automation. Humans still drive everything. Efficiency improves, but the cost curve does not change.</div>
          <div class="type-metrics">
            <div class="type-metric">Moderate efficiency gains</div>
            <div class="type-metric">Same staffing model</div>
            <div class="type-metric">Incremental improvement</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="type-stage exec-reveal">
          <div class="type-badge">3</div>
          <div class="type-name">AI-Native</div>
          <div class="type-desc">AI agents are first-class members of the workforce. They own tasks, manage queues, maintain records, and handle communications. Humans focus on care and judgment. This is where Machina takes you.</div>
          <div class="type-metrics">
            <div class="type-metric">Flat headcount at scale</div>
            <div class="type-metric">Expanding margins</div>
            <div class="type-metric">Defensible moat</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .exec-type-journey-section {
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 40px 40px 120px;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .type-journey {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-mid), var(--navy));
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 52px 48px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .type-journey::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--coral), var(--gold), var(--green));
  }

  .type-journey-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.85rem;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .type-journey-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--gray-300);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    max-width: 640px;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .type-stages {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .type-stages::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50px;
    left: 16.5%;
    right: 16.5%;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--coral), var(--gold), var(--green));
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .type-stage {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0 20px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .type-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    border: 2px solid;
  }

  .type-stage:nth-child(1) .type-badge {
    background: rgba(255,107,107,0.08);
    border-color: rgba(255,107,107,0.3);
    color: var(--coral);
  }

  .type-stage:nth-child(2) .type-badge {
    background: rgba(240,180,41,0.08);
    border-color: rgba(240,180,41,0.3);
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .type-stage:nth-child(3) .type-badge {
    background: rgba(6,214,160,0.08);
    border-color: rgba(6,214,160,0.3);
    color: var(--green);
  }

  .type-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .type-stage:nth-child(1) .type-name { color: var(--coral); }
  .type-stage:nth-child(2) .type-name { color: var(--gold); }
  .type-stage:nth-child(3) .type-name { color: var(--green); }

  .type-desc {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--gray-300);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .type-metrics {
    margin-top: 16px;
    padding-top: 14px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  }

  .type-metric {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    padding: 4px 0;
  }

  .type-stage:nth-child(1) .type-metric { color: rgba(255,107,107,0.7); }
  .type-stage:nth-child(2) .type-metric { color: rgba(240,180,41,0.7); }
  .type-stage:nth-child(3) .type-metric { color: rgba(6,214,160,0.8); }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .type-stages {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 28px;
    }

    .type-stages::before {
      display: none;
    }

    .type-journey {
      padding: 36px 24px;
    }

    .exec-type-journey-section {
      padding: 20px 24px 80px;
    }
  }
</style>
